{"tid":2267511,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【世衛總幹事譚德塞曾接觸確診者，未有病徵 正自我隔離】","createTime":"2020-11-02T06:32:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T06:33:11.000Z","uid":120499,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"042b63f73b8a2598ade3084b1839f3735b836e55","tid":2267511,"uid":120499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T06:32:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/265495733544884/posts/3418449161582843/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F265495733544884%2Fposts%2F3418449161582843%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxaooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=3447883a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/265495733544884/posts/3418449161582843/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n世界衛生組織總幹事譚德塞週一(2日)在Twitter發帖，表示自己曾接觸新冠病毒確診者，目前身體情況良好，未有任何病徵，未來一段時間會自我隔離，並跟從世衛指引在家工作。<br />\n<br />\n他之後又補充，會和世衛同仁繼續團結其他合作夥伴，一同拯救生命及保護弱小。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞在中國武漢爆發疫情初期，一直被批評偏袒中國，及遲遲不把新冠疫情列為全球大流行，引發全球網民聯署要求他辭職。譚德塞曾指控台灣向他發動惡意攻擊和種族歧視。<br />\n<br />\n#世衛譚德塞<br />\n#種族歧視<br />\n#武漢肺炎<br />\n<br />\nRest in Pieces <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3611db5205b7aa928e0a546d320f6f115c34c6c","tid":2267511,"uid":38982,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T06:33:11.000Z","msg":"苦肉計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}